To fetch Reconciliation Reports from Mercado Pago into Google Sheets using Google Apps Script.

https://www.mercadopago.com.mx/developers/es/guides/manage-account/reconciliation-reports/

Requires an access-token.

Found under "Credentials". See https://imgur.com/yZahXV7.

The API creates reports asynchronously.

Steps to download report:
1. Send request to create report.
2. Check is report is ready.
3. Download report.
